PouikPouik tout le monde! 
On se retrouve tout à l'heure pour l'#happyhour des débuts de semaines, -1€ sur la #pinte de #biere ou de sirop, de 17 à 21 heures, et une initiation au jeu #munchkins ! Choisis ta version : #chtulu ? #starwars ? 
Mercredi, c'est la #cocktailparty avec les cocktails sans alcool à 1e de moins et ceux avec alcool à 2e de moins! Let's try them!  #tasty 
Jeudi, #freeplay , on s'amuse entre potos et on relativise : C'EST BIENTÔT LE #weekend ! 
Vendredi, c'est l'heure du #tournoi ! Mouton, écureuil,  cheval ou poule, choisis ton animal et passe la ligne d'arrivée en premier avec #ultimatechickenhorse sur la switch! Piège les autres challengers, et gagne!

Samedi, on bouge son boule et on dans en rythme sur la #justdance2019 party! Let's moooove! 
Dimanche, on chill et on se prépare pour la semaine d'après ! ❤

caption.text:
Hey everybody! It's the last day of September so you know what that means lol; I present along with a few good friends, a prompt list! Centered around Smash Bros, here are some prompts for you to use at your leisure. They don't necessarily have to be the character, just solely based around it. (But of course fanart of the character is far game lol)
.
A few notes, Mii Fighter is for you to decide whether you choose Brawler, Gunner or Swordfighter and it can be your Mii if you have one, or even a Persona based on a Mii Fighter. (Sans is also fair game because he's a skin. Any character that can be assembled via Mii Fighter Costume is fair game to draw.)
.
The Choice slot for Day 31 is free for you to choose a character! Whether it be an upcoming DLC like Terry or a character on the roster that isn't on the Prompt List, you can draw.
.
There are no rules besides have fun, do as much as you can, and don't forget to include the tag #smashtober_ (yes, with the underscore) and prompt list if you're participating. Good luck!
.

Dato del día 😄

Pokémon Let's Go Pikachu e Eevee, uno de los remakes menos esperados hasta el momento. Es un spin-off por parte de Nintendo, nos sorprendió con este juego, ya que no hay habilidades, ni crianza y su sistema de captura es parecida a Pokémon GO, la famosa aplicación para celulares.

En mi opinión, este remake fue una primera prueba para aprovechar las capacidades de la Nintendo Switch, muy buen juego para pasar el tiempo y recordar viejos tiempos a los primeros juegos de Pokémon.

Layden departs Playstation.

#Playstation announced via twitter that current worldwide studio chairman Shawn Layden will be leaving  Sony Interactive Entertainment after over 30 years with the company. “It is with great emotion that we announce that Worldwide Studios Chairman Shawn Layden will be departing SIE. His visionary leadership will be greatly missed. We wish him success in future endeavors and are deeply grateful for his years of service. Thanks for everything, Shawn!” His name and face became synonymous with Playstation through his #E3 presentations since he took the role of Worldwide Studio Chairman in 2016. There is no mention from Layden"s side in the departure as of yet.

#Gamefemerides
Hace 25 años es lanzado DOOM II. Es un juego de disparos en primera persona, el segundo título de id Software de la franquicia @doom . Fue originalmente lanzado para computadoras MS-DOS en 1994, y para Mactintosh en 1995. A diferencia de Doom, que solo estuvo disponible como shareware y por correo, Doom II fue un lanzamiento comercial en tiendas. Master Levels for Doom II, un paquete de expansión que incluye 21 nuevos niveles, fue lanzado el 26 de diciembre de 1995 por id Software. 
Debido a su éxito y popularidad, Doom II fue luego lanzado para Game Boy Advance de Nintendo en 2002, Xbox Live Arcade en 2010, y para @Nintendo Switch, @PlayStation 4, y @Xbox One en 2019. La liberación del código fuente del Doom original ha participado que se portee a otras plataformas.

I think Link’s Awakening might be the fastest I’ve ever finished a game recently. I’ve only had it for about a week and a half, and I’m already almost done with it. Though, I consider that a good thing! Most of the games I play are long JRPGs, so it’s nice to have something different every once in a while. I also just REALLY love Zelda games. They did an amazing job with this remake, and I highly recommend it to other Zelda fans out there! 🔷
